                {
                    "name": "Brand of the Impenitent",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "<b>Frequency</b> once per day; <b>Effect</b> The balisse marks an evil creature within its confessor\u2019s aura as irredeemable. It can only do so after a failed attempt to convince the creature to repent. The touched creature takes a \u20131 status penalty to AC and saves, reduces its resistances by 2, and gains weakness 2 to good damage. The duration depends on the target\u2019s DC 26 Will save.<br/> <b>Critical Success</b> The creature is unaffected.<br/> <b>Success</b> The duration is 1 round.<br/> <b>Failure</b> The duration is 1 day.<br/> <b>Critical Failure</b> The duration is permanent.",
